Royal Envoy			KEY:Purple Dragon Knight ~ Royal Envoy			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.128	DESC:A Purple Dragon knight serves as an envoy of the Cormyrean crown. Knights of high standing are expected to conduct themselves with grace. You gain proficiency in the Persuasion skill. If you are already proficient in it, you gain proficiency in one of the following skills of your choice: Animal Handling, Insight, Intimidation, or Performance. Your proficiency bonus is doubled for any ability check you make that uses Persuasion. You receive this benefit regardless of the skill proficiency you gain from this feature.
Inspiring Surge		KEY:Purple Dragon Knight ~ Inspiring Surge		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.128	DESC:When you use your Action Surge feature, you can choose		DESC: one |PREVARLTEQ:FighterLVL,16	DESC: two |PREVARGTEQ:FighterLVL,17	DESC:creature(s) within 60 feet of you that is allied with you. That creature can make one melee or ranged weapon attack with its reaction, provided that it can see or hear you.
Bulwark			KEY:Purple Dragon Knight ~ Bulwark				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.128	DESC:When you decide to use Indomitable to reroll an Intelligence, a Wisdom, or a Charisma saving throw and you aren't incapacitated, you can choose one ally within 60 feet of you that also failed its saving throw against the same effect. If that creature can see or hear you, it can reroll its saving throw and must use the new roll.

