Oath Of The Crown		SOURCEPAGE:p.132		KEY:Sacred Oath ~ Oath Of The Crown			SORTKEY:Class	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Sacred Oath		DESC:The Oath of the Crown is sworn to the ideals of civilization, be it the spirit of a nation, fealty to a sovereign, or service to a deity of law and rulership. The paladins who swear this oath dedicate themselves to serving society and, in particular, the just laws that hold society together. These paladins are the watchful guardians on the walls, standing agai nst the chaotic tides of barbarism that threaten to tear down all that civilization has built, and are commonly known as guardians, exemplars, or sentinels. Often, paladins who swear this oath are members of an order of knighthood in service to a nation or a sovereign, and undergo their oath as part of their admission to the order's ranks.	DESC:&nl; TENETS OF THE CROWN - The tenets of the Oath of the Crown are often set by the sovereign to which their oath is sworn, but generally emphasize the following tenets. Law. The law is paramount. It is the mortar that holds the stones of civilization together, and it must be respected. Loyalty. Your word is your bond. Without loyalty, oaths and laws are meaningless. Courage. You must be willing to do what needs to be done for the sake of order, even in the face of overwhelming odds. If you don't act, then who will? Responsibility. You must deal with the consequences of your actions, and you are responsible for fulfilling your duties and obligations.	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Paladin=1|Command,Compelled Duel|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=3	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Paladin=2|Warding Bond,Zone Of Truth|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=5	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Paladin=3|Aura Of Vitality,Spirit Guardians|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=9	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Paladin=4|Banishment,Guardian Of Faith|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=13	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Paladin=5|Circle Of Power,Geas|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=17	SPELLLEVEL:CLASS|Paladin=1|Command,Compelled Duel|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=3	SPELLLEVEL:CLASS|Paladin=2|Warding Bond,Zone Of Truth|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=5	SPELLLEVEL:CLASS|Paladin=3|Aura Of Vitality,Spirit Guardians|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=9	SPELLLEVEL:CLASS|Paladin=4|Banishment,Guardian Of Faith|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=13	SPELLLEVEL:CLASS|Paladin=5|Circle Of Power,Geas|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=17	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Oath Of The Crown ~ Channel Divinity Champion Challenge|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Oath Of The Crown ~ Channel Divinity Turn The Tide|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Oath Of The Crown ~ Divine Allegiance|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=7	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Oath Of The Crown ~ Unyielding Spirit|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=15	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Oath Of The Crown ~ Exalted Champion|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=20

# Oath Of The Crown
Channel Divinity: Champion Challenge	KEY:Oath Of The Crown ~ Channel Divinity Champion Challenge		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.131	DESC:You issue a challenge that compels other creatures to do battle with you. Each creature of your choice that you can see within 30 feet of you must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a creature can't willingly move more than 30 feet away from you. This effect ends on the creature if you are incapacitated or die or if the creature is moved more than 30 feet away from you.
Channel Divinity: Turn The Tide		KEY:Oath Of The Crown ~ Channel Divinity Turn The Tide		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.131	DESC:As a bonus action, you can bolster injured creatures with your Channel Divinity. Each creature of your choice that can hear you within 30 feet of you regains hit points equal to 1d6 +your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1) if it has no more than half of its hit points.
Divine Allegiance					KEY:Oath Of The Crown ~ Divine Allegiance					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.131	DESC:Starting at 7th level, when a creature within 5 feet of you takes damage, you can use your reaction to magically substitute your own health for that of the target creature, causing that creature not to take the damage. Instead, you take the damage. This damage to you can't be reduced or prevented in any way.
Unyielding Spirit					KEY:Oath Of The Crown ~ Unyielding Spirit					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.131	DESC:Starting at 15th level, you have advantage on saving throws to avoid becoming paralyzed or stunned.
Exalted Champion					KEY:Oath Of The Crown ~ Exalted Champion					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.131	DESC:At 20th level, your presence on the field of battle is an inspiration to those dedicated to your cause. You can use your action to gain the following benefits for 1 hour: You have resistance to bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage from nonmagical weapons. * Your allies have advantage on death saving throws while within 30 feet of you. You have advantage on Wisdom saving throws, as do your allies within 30 feet of you. This effect ends early if you are incapacitated or die. Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.

